parameters:
Memimi: How about that... I've done it... Are you
satisfied...? Hey, are you satisfied...? Huh...?

Cerburus Octopus: He's, he's pissed... Naturally, no one
would want to face that... It's scary...

Shark Broccoli: You did well, Duke Shark... Calm down...
Rest your heart...

Bunny-chan: Duke Shark-sama has completed the task, so the
rematch for Monster Fight is now set! The schedule will
follow... Goodbye for now~...

Cerburus Octopus: See ya... I'll win again next time, of
course! Later!
Shark Broccoli: We should go too... Let's leave him alone...

Although Memimi had inflicted a huge wound on her own honor
and social standing, she perfectly met the conditions set by
Cerburus Octopus and secured the right to a rematch...

Memimi: ...How am I supposed to face school from
tomorrow...? I can't imagine what my school life will be
like from now on... Ugh... Ugh...
